ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 29th day of October, 2015, the Application for Leave to File Original Process and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus are GRANTED. The Court of Common Pleas of Montgomery County is DIRECTED to adjudicate Petitioner’s pending filing within 90 days. The Prothonotary is DIRECTED to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
